                        "description":  "For up to 1 minute with concentration, your eyes become inky voids. On the initial cast and again with a Magic action on later turns, choose Asleep, Panicked, or Sickened for one visible creature within 60 feet; a creature that succeeds on a Wisdom save against this casting cannot be targeted by it again.",
